from PIL import Image, ImageDraw, ImageFont
import numpy as np

## 원하는 결과 가져오기
json_data=json.loads(response.data)
dict_data=json_data["return_object"]["data"]

## 이미지에 객체별 표시하기
img = Image.open("./data/거리1.jpg")
font=ImageFont.truetype("c:/windows/fonts/gulim.ttc", 15)
draw = ImageDraw.Draw(img)

for cls in dict_data:
    gubun=cls['class']
    x=int(cls['x']);y=int(cls['y']);w=int(cls['width']);h=int(cls['height'])
    
    if gubun =='person':
        color=(255,0,0)
    elif gubun =='car':
        color=(0,255,0)
    else:
        color=(0,0,255)

    draw.line([(x, y), (x, y+h), (x+w, y+h), (x+w, y), (x, y)], fill=color, width=2)
    draw.text((x, y-15), gubun, font=font, fill=color)
